{"type": "article", "id": 22184, "title": "「拥抱」戒指", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-14T08:23:40Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 186, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702133910vnXkfA34EoJUWT07.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>那些大同小异总是比拼克拉数的钻戒是不是已经看腻了？其实表达爱意有时候并不是用钱砸出来的，稍稍花一些小心思便能与众不同。比如香港设计师 INNO.PARK 带来的这款名为「Hand In Love」的情侣对戒，好似一个相依相偎的拥抱。环抱状的样子运用了拟人手法，925 银涂上玫瑰金或是铂金的镀层，小巧别致，质感也不错。即便分隔两地，带着这枚小小的戒指，恋人之间也能感受到如拥抱般的温暖。售价 68 美元（约合人民币 444 元），<a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/shop/design/hand-in-love-inno-park-05-06-2015/\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133907sBpwqajzFT3tDAZv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75794621\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133907ShfJl9EHzuNcmFQZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75794621\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133908S9YVWOCZMjBm7T1i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75794621\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133909qOJp1HblVaB4r5PN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59351852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133909V8t17sbjI54zYgyi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75794621\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n"}